  "page": "Brandon Norrey (son of Brandon)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Brandon (disambiguation)\">Brandon (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Norrey\" title=\"House Norrey\"><img alt=\"House Norrey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/50px-House_Norrey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/75px-House_Norrey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/100px-House_Norrey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Brandon Norrey</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Norrey\" title=\"House Norrey\"><img alt=\"House Norrey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/50px-House_Norrey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/75px-House_Norrey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/85/House_Norrey.svg/100px-House_Norrey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nBrandon the Younger</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Norrey\" title=\"House Norrey\">House Norrey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">Northern mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Norrey\" title=\"Brandon Norrey\">Brandon Norrey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Brandon Norrey</b>, called <b>Brandon the Younger</b>, is the son and heir of <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Norrey\" title=\"Brandon Norrey\">Brandon Norrey</a>, the Norrey, the clan chief of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Norrey\" title=\"House Norrey\">House Norrey</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">mountain clan</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brandon_Norrey_(son_of_Brandon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brandon_Norrey_(son_of_Brandon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Because <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Norrey\" title=\"Brandon Norrey\">his father</a> is too old to go on campaign,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Brandon joins the army of <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>. Brandon insists that \"<a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Arya Stark</a>\" be rescued from <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brandon_Norrey_(son_of_Brandon)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspa